featured_reviews.review_id:
In 2009 We used to perform salat-uz-zuhr in Masjid Abdullah when we were in Noor school.
Ma shaa Allah! Women section was quite spacious.
When i was in school i used to perform salah but not in a correct manner not in a way of our beloved prophet  taught the salaf-us-saliheen as he  said "pray as you have seen me praying". (Bukhari:7246)
I'm writing this just to advice you all to pray for everyone's hidayah if they're not praying salah like they should pray as our prophet  taught.
Alhamdulillah, in the year 2015 Allah has guided me to the truth, to the path of pious predecessors (Salaf us saliheen) And I've been praying Salah as our beloved prophet  taught and striving upon salafiyyah.
So we should keep asking Allah for the guidance and keep striving, As he is the only one who guides.
l lh l llh mHmd rswl llh
